# PD_Boundary

## Overview
This repository, `PD_Boundary`, is designed to configure a test enviroment to test ssh with credential injection being accessed by multi hop workers.

#
## Installation
To get started, clone the repository and install the required dependencies:
Boundary ClI
Boundary Desktop
Vault ClI

create a .env file with all the relevant information (copy the .env.example and change the correct values)

## Usage

### Setup
to use this lab run the 0_setup.sh script

```bash
chmod +x 0_setup.sh
./0_setup.sh
```

### Destroy
to stop using this lab and destroy the config (so you can reuse it again another day)
```bash
chmod +x 99_destroy-lab.sh
./99_destroy-lab.sh
```


